-- China National Petroleum Targets `Noticeable' Boost in Overseas Operations
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-28T00:33:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/china-national-petroleum-targets-noticeable-boost-in-overseas-operations.html

          
          
             China National Petroleum Corp.
targets a “noticeable increase” in its overseas operations in
the next decade, the Beijing-based company said in a statement
posted on its website today.  
 The state-owned company will focus on its core oil and gas
business in the next five years, it said.  
          
          


  


        